description: - Develop and maintain high-quality Flutter applications for both iOS and Android.- Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define, design, and ship new features.

Develop backend components using Django framework.
Collaborate with front-end developers to integrate user-facing elements with server-side logic.

Collaborate with cross-functional teams including developers, and product managers, to ensure design coherence.
Prepare a clean UI/UX of all the problems, interviews, suggested solutions and rough user flows
Prepare Wireframe and visual mockups with working prototypes
Conduct user research to understand the user needs, preferences, and behavior.
Conduct various meetings with supervisors and project managers to accomplish design-driven development.

Manage and optimize our existing deployment process using GitHub Actions.
